  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC460">
        <l>orumai cuṭṭiya peyarnilaik kiḷavi</l>
	<l>paṉmaik kāku miṭaṉumā ruṇṭē.</l>
            </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/257/mode/1up">257</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/258/mode/1up">258</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ituvum pālvaḻu amaikkiṉṟatu.</p>
<p>urai : orumai cuṭṭi niṉṟa peyarc collum paṉmaikoṇṭu muṭiyum iṭaṉum uṭaittu eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC460-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'aṅkaluḻ māmai yakutai tantai</l>
<l>yaṇṇal yāṉai yaṭupōrc cōḻar'</l></lg>
<p>eṉa varum.</p>
<p>itaṉuḷ, 'tantai' eṉaniṉṟa orumai muṟaippeyar, 'cōḻar' eṉṉum paṉmaikoṇṭu muṭintamaiyiṉ, vaḻūuvēyeṉiṉum amaiyum eṉpatu ;</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC460-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'yāṉem mūrpukuval'</l></lg>
<p>eṉpatum atu.	(64)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

